{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removePack:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","text":"MLNOfflinePack","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pack","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","preciseIdentifier":"c:MLNOfflineStorage.h@T@MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The offline pack to remove.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"pack"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The completion handler to call once the pack has been","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"removed. This handler is executed asynchronously on the main queue.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"completion"}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As soon as this method is called on a pack, the pack becomes invalid; any"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"attempt to send it a message will result in an exception being thrown. If an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"error occurs and the pack cannot be removed, do not attempt to reuse the pack","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object. Instead, if you need continued access to the pack, suspend all packs","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and use the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/reloadPacks","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" method to obtain valid pointers to all the packs.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To detect when any call to this method results in a pack being removed, observe","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"KVO change notifications on the shared offline storage object’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" key"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path. Removals from that array result in an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSKeyValueChangeRemoval"},{"text":" change.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When you remove an offline pack, any resources that are required by that pack,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"but not other packs, become eligible for deletion from offline storage. Because"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the backing store used for offline storage is also used as a general purpose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"cache for map resources, such resources may not be immediately removed if the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"implementation determines that they remain useful for general performance of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the map.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflineStorage(im)removePack:withCompletionHandler:","title":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Unregisters the given offline pack and allows resources that are no longer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"required by any remaining packs to be potentially freed.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/removePack:withCompletionHandler:"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/removepack:withcompletionhandler:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage/removePack:withCompletionHandler:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/removePack:withCompletionHandler:","title":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Unregisters the given offline pack and allows resources that are no longer","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"required by any remaining packs to be potentially freed.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/removepack:withcompletionhandler:","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","title":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"A block to be called once an offline pack has been completely invalidated and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"removed.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackremovalcompletionhandler","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage/reloadPacks":{"abstract":[{"text":"Forcibly, asynchronously reloads the ","type":"text"},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property. At some point after this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method is called, the pointer values of the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" objects in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property change, even if the underlying data for these packs has not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"changed. If this method is called while a pack is actively downloading, the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"behavior is undefined.","type":"text"}],"title":"reloadPacks","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"reloadPacks","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/reloadpacks","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/reloadPacks","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","abstract":[{"text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its ","type":"text"},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","role":"symbol","title":"MLNOfflineStorage","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflineStorage","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePack","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNOfflinePack","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","isActive":true},{"text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a region offline to a local database.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"}}}